Package: metayer
Title: Tooling for package development
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Dustin", "Lennon", , "dustin.lennon@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-8558-8765"))
Description: metayer provides miscellaneous tooling for package development.  It currently
    enhances vignettes written in jupyter lab; allows folding of cli code into logger; adds
    a hierarchical storage environment; and provides a few utility methods for working with
    environments.
